<h1><%= @fellow.first_name %>&rsquo;s Career Dashboard</h1>

<%= link_to 'View profile details', fellow_profile_path %>

<h3>Career Progress</h3>
<div id="career-tracker">
  <div class="tracker-item start"><h4>START</h4><p class="big-symbol">&#10132;</p></div>
  <div class="tracker-item"><input id="career-item-01" type="checkbox" checked><label for="career-item-01"><h4>1</h4><p>I know my strengths and values and can communicate my story</p></label></div>
  <div class="tracker-item"><input id="career-item-02" type="checkbox" checked><label for="career-item-02"><h4>2</h4><p>I understand what career-accelerating means and what career paths can look like</p></label></div>
  <div class="tracker-item"><input id="career-item-03" type="checkbox" checked><label for="career-item-03"><h4>3</h4><p>I have a career roadmap with professional goals and a plan</p></label></div>
  <div class="tracker-item"><input id="career-item-04" type="checkbox"><label for="career-item-04"><h4>4</h4><p>My resume is strong and ready to send to potential employers</p></label></div>
  <div class="tracker-item"><input id="career-item-05" type="checkbox"><label for="career-item-05"><h4>5</h4><p>My LinkedIn profile is updated and professional</p></label></div>
  <div class="tracker-item"><input id="career-item-06" type="checkbox"><label for="career-item-06"><h4>6</h4><p>My social media is scrubbed of content I don’t want potential employers to see</p></div>
  <div class="tracker-item"><input id="career-item-07" type="checkbox"><label for="career-item-07"><h4>7</h4><p>I know my elevator pitch like the back of my hand</p></label></div>
  <div class="tracker-item"><input id="career-item-08" type="checkbox"><label for="career-item-08"><h4>8</h4><p>I have a networking strategy and a system for keeping track of opportunities and people I meet</p></label></div>
  <div class="tracker-item"><input id="career-item-09" type="checkbox"><label for="career-item-09"><h4>9</h4><p>I’ve had informational interviews with professionals in my desired career field</p></label></div>
  <div class="tracker-item"><input id="career-item-10" type="checkbox"><label for="career-item-10"><h4>10</h4><p>I am ready to ace a job interview</p></label></div>
  <div class="tracker-item"><input id="career-item-11" type="checkbox"><label for="career-item-11"><h4>11</h4><p>I've reflected on what I want to look for next and researched the field</p></label></div>
  <div class="tracker-item"><input id="career-item-12" type="checkbox"><label for="career-item-12"><h4>12</h4><p>I've made a shortlist of positions and/or employers</p></label></div>
</div>
<h3>Active Opportunities</h3>

<% if @fellow.fellow_opportunities.empty? %>
  <p>None at this time.</p>
<% else %>
  <ul class="fellow-opportunities">
    <% @fellow.fellow_opportunities.each do |candidate| %>
      <li><%= link_to candidate.opportunity.formatted_name, fellow_opportunity_path(candidate) %></li>
    <% end %>
  </ul>
<% end %>